<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id45e1cd72-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s4902"><num value="4902">§ 4902.</num><heading> Liability of partners</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any number of persons doing business in copartnership at any one place shall be required to pay but one special tax.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id45e1cd73-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736">Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68A/593">68A Stat. 593</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
